sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant AuthUI as Auth UI
    participant System
    participant Database

    Note over Student,AuthUI: UC-01: Register
    
    Student->>AuthUI: Enters email & password
    AuthUI->>System: register(email, password)
    System->>System: validateInputFormat(email, password)
    
    alt Invalid Input (e.g. Weak Password)
        System-->>AuthUI: Error: "Weak password or invalid format"
        AuthUI-->>Student: Show error & reload form
    else Input Valid
        System->>Database: checkEmailUnique(email)
        Database-->>System: isUnique?
        
        alt Email Already Registered
            System-->>AuthUI: Error: "Email already registered"
            AuthUI-->>Student: Show "Log in here" link
        else Email is Unique
            System->>Database: createAccount(email, hash(password))
            Database-->>System: accountId
            System->>Database: createStudentProfile(accountId, xp: 0)
            Database-->>System: success
            System->>System: Create authenticated session
            System-->>AuthUI: Registration Successful
            AuthUI-->>Student: Redirect to Student Dashboard
        end
    end